page.title: 20THE DOMESDAY PROJECT
page.content: The Domesday Project for this area was compiled by the following members of Thorpe St Andrews School: Joanne Bucknell, Susan Howe, Stephanie Mills, Nichola Parker, Michael Palmer, Billy Waters,Rebekah Beschorner, Luisa Copping, Janine Latham, Rebecca Lincoln,Karen Sinclair, Emma Smith, Melanie Varvel,Giles Conneely, Howard Malin, Kirstyn Allen, Karen Oldman, Kay Whysall, Keith Ball, Douglas Jones, Adrian Lee, Lisa Artherton, Clare Burdett, Rebecca Dowson, Diane Townshend, Amanda Woodcock, Simon Grand, Julian Mabey, Charles Smith, Justine Moore. The photographs were taken by Charles Smith. The teacher in charge was Mr. Peter J. Smith.
